rComments: A really nice guy who will help students if necessary.  The 1st test was easy, after that, they were ridiculously hard but generously curved.  In essence, the lectures did not adequately prepare us for the exams.  On the bright side, because of curving, its easy to get at least B overall.

He is probably one of the worst professor in UIUC. Does not know how to use the blackboard to teach math. His slides are just copies from the textbook which are equally bad as the professor himself. I passed this course on my own. The TA's do a better job than him.
